{"tid":1704651,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"我係波鞋撚 呢張文宣炒咗車","createTime":"2019-11-10T18:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T19:58:31.000Z","uid":159172,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c70bd1c0a254af2aba4aa97d35f10e377977dd37","tid":1704651,"uid":159172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mEiSnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mEiSnE.jpg&h=6bd3c253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果睇下鞋底紋理同形狀<br />\n我斷定係一對Ultra boost相信大家都會同意。<br />\n<br />\n歷代出嘅ultra Boost 1.0去到4.0，<br />\n每一代<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>[black]黑色[/black]</strong></span>鞋面嘅話，鞋底都<span style=\"font-size: large;\">必然係[black]黑色[/black]</span><br />\n<br />\n印像中出過有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>[black]黑色鞋面[/black]</strong></span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>加白色鞋底</em></span></strong>嘅。以我認知我得三款<br />\n<br />\n1: Hybeast X UltraBoost 1.0 Uncaged<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZtr1gF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZtr1gF.jpg&h=a0853930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. Undefeated Ultra boost 4.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/diM5xor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdiM5xor.jpg&h=366928e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. UltraBoost 4.0 &ldquo;Orca&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07t0mgR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07t0mgR.jpg&h=805c7d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 萬幾銀一對正常人唔係會捨着。仲要係白色鞋踭唔會係全黑。<br />\n2.鞋頭會有一項好大嘅白色&quot;UNDEFEATED&quot;字樣。<br />\n3. Orca 嘅三間鞋框係白包唔會係全黑色<br />\n<br />\n所以我判斷可能性得兩個：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周同學對嘢一係老翻，一係入咗對Orca就自訂剪框/噴框。</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">換言之呢對嘢唔係市面上咁容易買到，要做假嘅機會好低。對鞋都相信係啱啱新落地無耐，所以離遠睇似係白色都好正常。</span><br />\n<br />\n點都好做偵探嘅時間已經過啦，大家早啲瞓聽日再打過啦。<br />\n<br />\n就算張圖點樣都好。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周同學唔係失足避催淚彈跌落去。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢係被政權推下去。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仆個街佢同我同齡，你班黑警一定要同我冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，報仇。</span>"},{"pid":"06aba53e6fb1a30a0040b3ee39ec9ca9e4f203df","tid":1704651,"uid":136467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stockx.com/adidas-ultra-boost-4pt0-core-black\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstockx.com%2Fadidas-ultra-boost-4pt0-core-black&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a9f7e377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stockx.com/adidas-ultra-boost-4pt0-core-black</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c6cf66c1ff247702da446c4505fba1fb302938","tid":1704651,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"香港人不忘記不原諒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲俾班曱甴咁開心結婚？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c7d5bf15ce7125e8ba198b1c2189526daa002f0","tid":1704651,"uid":211829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06aba53e6fb1a30a0040b3ee39ec9ca9e4f203df","tid":1704651,"uid":136467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stockx.com/adidas-ultra-boost-4pt0-core-black\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstockx.com%2Fadidas-ultra-boost-4pt0-core-black&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a9f7e377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stockx.com/adidas-ultra-boost-4pt0-core-black</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi